description.text:
Here introdused a large collection of logos of famous rock bands. All logos assembled in the OpenScad library logo_lib.scad (rus_logo_lib.scad - for Russian bands). Use these pictures on your own. For example, I created a key chains. Any user can expand the library, and share it! I used Inkscape to OpenSCAD converter (<a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:25036" >http://www.thingiverse.com/thing:25036</a>) to create a 3D-model of vector graphics.<br />
In this time the next bands are avaible:<br />
